*Obojica su odlučili da se vrate kući.* (Both of them decided to go back home.)

*Oni su obojica bili zadovoljni sa svojim odlukom.* (Both of them were satisfied with their decision.)

*Obojica su dolazili svakog dana.* (Both of them were coming every day.)

*Obojica su hteli da odmore.* (Both of them wanted to rest.)

*Obojica su otišla u park.* (Both of them went to the park.)

*Obojica su prešli ulicu.* (Both of them crossed the street.)

*Obojica su bila jako umorna.* (Both of them were very tired.)

*Obojica su bili srećni.* (Both of them were happy.)